title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ members who've signed up for this month (December 12 - January 10) will also receive:

— Access to the new Vinewood Club Garage
— The new Declasse Impaler LX
— Exclusive clothing
— 2X GTA$ and RP on Drift Races
— 1.5X GTA$ on Tow Stick Service Salvage Value
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel any time. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
